reviewText: If your into the royal family: this one is a must. Time line-from birth to Royal Jubilee. Charles fans get a good summery of his life give in the time frame mentioned. Best of all this dvd DIDN'T HAVE TO BE CONVERTED TO US FORMATE. I was able to play it like a dvd from the states-phew big relief because I did want to pay extra to have it transferred in US form. This subject is very pleased.
